text: Ærest on Baddanbyrg westweard norðriht on ðone stocc.
Of ðam stocce to wearge dune betweone ðe twege beorges.
Eastriht andlang dice on ðone fulan wylle.
Of ðam wylle on foxhylle norðweard on ðone ealdan heortwæg on ðone wylle.
Of ðam wylle on ðone ealde heortsole.
Of ðam heortsole on ðone beorge.
Of ðam beorge on ðone graf.
Of ðam grafe on wyðigwylle.
Of ðam wylle on ðone stodfald.
Of ðam stodfalde on ðæt stangedelf.
Ðæt on mæres wylle.
Andlang mæres dene on Weaclinga stræt.
Andlang stræte ðat it cymð to ðam ricgwege.
Andlang ricgweges ðæt it cymð toemnes Doddanforda, forðriht on ðone stocc.
Of ðam stocce on ðene broc.
Andlang broces toemnes Niwanham.
Andlang slædes on ða dic æt ðam grafe.
Eastweard andlang dice ðæt it cymð æt ðam grafe.
Westweard on ðene ford.
Up andlang broces ðæt it cyme toemnes Baddanbyrig.
Westweard of ðam broce æft on Baddanbyrig westwearde.
